			<section class="comment-content comment">
				<p>Generally speaking, a preprocessor will increase the speed of your site, assuming you have the preprocessor compress/minify your code. Because the CSS is created before it&#8217;s ever requested by the user, there is absolutely zero slowdown on the user&#8217;s end for that step.</p>
