                              <p class="post-title">
                  <a href="index.html?p=228" title="Permalink to: jQuery-Based Popout Ad: Part 3">
                    jQuery-Based Popout Ad: Part 3                  </a>
                </p>
              
              
              
                              <p class="post-excerpt">The previous article in this series explained how to take CSS- and XHTML-based advertisement we had developed and animate it using the jQuery JavaScript library. Today, we're going to expand our jQuery a bit to make our ad a little bit more user-friendly. <a href="index.html?p=228" class="more-link" title="Permalink to: jQuery-Based Popout Ad: Part 3">Read more →</a></p>
              
              
              
              
              
